  "text": "Elimination Rules : respectively must be the most recent non discarded [CITATION_1] assumptions occurring in the proof. When we apply one of these rules on step n and discard an assumption on step m, we also discard all formulae from m to n − 1. We will write [m − (n−1)] to indicate this situation.",
